{"tid":861172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國安顧問：將更強硬對待中國　促習近平下月坦誠討論調整國家行為","createTime":"2018-10-14T02:10:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T00:28:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"62a627aafdb01527984c0ac407ae3ec2c7322454","tid":861172,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"美國安顧問：將更強硬對待中國　促習近平下月坦誠討論調整國家行為<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181013/s00005/1539434887079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181013%2Fs00005%2F1539434887079&d=MQUFF1JQbQWlVJcwYZXh9E%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0bdc4c25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181013%2Fs00005%2F1539434887079&h=3f7f2d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181013/s00005/1539434887079</a><br />\n<br />\n中美貿易戰愈演愈烈，美國國家安全顧問博爾頓（John Bolton）表示，美方將更強硬對待中國，中方需調整在貿易、軍事、政治及國際關係方面等行為。他又稱，希望在下月舉行的G20峰會上，中國國家主席習近平能「坦率認真地討論」這些議題。<br />\n<br />\n中美軍艦上月30日（上周日）在南海幾乎相撞，雙方最接近時僅相距約41米。博爾頓在當地時間周五（12日）播出的電台訪問中形容，有關情況「危險」，指中國要明白，南海不是中國的一個省，美國有決心保持國際航道開放。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">博爾頓又表示，中國靠違反國際貿易與商業常規，獲取可觀經濟及軍事力量，指若中方被放回「正確位置」，不能再竊取美方的科技，「他們的軍事力量會大減，中國引起的緊張局勢亦會變小」。<br />\n</span><br />\n美國總統特朗普周四（11日）接受霍士新聞（Fox News）訪問時稱，「中國人好日子過得太久」，自己對中國「還能做很多」。博爾頓表示，美方將中國視為「本世紀重大議題」，相信美國如此強硬對待中方，已令北京感到「困惑」（confused），「他們從未見過如此強硬的美國總統」。<span style=\"color: red;\">他期望中國國家主席習近平，下月出席在阿根廷舉行的G20峰會時，會就這些議題「坦率認真地討論」（talk turkey）。</span><br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"a459d2b0a5033ece626ffba16681c87f673fb2e6","tid":861172,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  強硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點解唔直接喺一大班記者面前直接屌鳩雜種  屌鳩蝗蟈 ? <br />\n<br />\n成日都係無會面既時候  透過傳媒「強硬」"},{"pid":"fffe9739106eb42389e9e8f6211f16f79eb79f16","tid":861172,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a459d2b0a5033ece626ffba16681c87f673fb2e6","tid":861172,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  強硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點解唔直接喺一大班記者面前直接屌鳩雜種  屌鳩蝗蟈 ? <br />\n<br />\n成日都係無會面既時候  透過傳媒「強硬」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:14:25.000Z","msg":"你走先"},{"pid":"74c1abb0395960d3b96340922ff47e0d0f8be366","tid":861172,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f89f9e266ac8aca07c60c95644cef323f3d460","tid":861172,"uid":81192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a459d2b0a5033ece626ffba16681c87f673fb2e6","tid":861172,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":22,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  強硬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   點解唔直接喺一大班記者面前直接屌鳩雜種  屌鳩蝗蟈 ? <br />\n<br />\n成日都係無會面既時候  透過傳媒「強硬」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:48:55.000Z","msg":"即係直接宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ae18ae166f2cb7cd455348b71a6354008e8ff4","tid":861172,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9fe1d69c8df1c3ae90dc74a134d5687b9489d1","tid":861172,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"中美吹水大會繼續進行"},{"pid":"cc4cb77fa36368ed1e1bca9d33b0923d162771a3","tid":861172,"uid":24980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T07:18:34.000Z